{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"573","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"勞動契約認定原則 許銘春：讓勞資有依循","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<div class='shareBar__info--author' style='margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 6px 0px; float: left; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); font-size: 13px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;LiHei Pro&quot;, 新細明體, PMingLiU, 新宋体, NSimSun, &quot;Apple LiGothic Medium&quot;, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class='fb-like facebook-holder fb_iframe_widget' data-action='like' data-href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/4175945' data-layout='button_count' data-share='true' data-show-faces='false' data-width='100' fb-iframe-plugin-query='action=like&amp;app_id=267846550050865&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F7307%2F4175945&amp;layout=button_count&amp;locale=zh_TW&amp;sdk=joey&amp;share=true&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=100' fb-xfbml-state='rendered' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2019-11-20 10:30</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中央社 記者吳欣紜台北<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日電</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>勞動部昨天發布「勞動契約認定指導原則」，盼供勞雇雙方檢視勞動契約關係，勞動部長許銘春今天表示，<span lang='EN-US'>25</span>項檢核事項能協助勞資政三方未來有依循。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>為避免雇主規避責任用承攬方式僱傭勞工，勞動部昨天發布「勞動契約認定指導原則」，並製作勞動契約從屬性判斷檢核表，詳列<span lang='EN-US'>25</span>項檢核事項，盼供勞雇雙方檢視勞動契約關係。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>許銘春今天在立法院社會福利及衛生環境委員會前接受媒體訪問指出，「勞動契約認定指導原則」是一個重要的行政指導，原則將歷來包含大法官解釋、法院判決及勞動部函釋做一個綜合整理。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>許銘春表示，勞動契約與其它勞資關係最大的差別就是有沒有指揮監督，這是從屬性的判斷，因此這次製作了從屬性的檢核表、詳列<span lang='EN-US'>25</span>項判斷關鍵，這對未來勞資政三方在認定是否為勞動契約有很大的幫助，也希望當勞資雙方如有對勞動契約有疑義時，可以用檢核表檢視、釐清爭議。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>許銘春指出，基於契約自由，在勞動現場勞動關係具有多樣性，但希望不管是承攬或是僱傭都應該要明確，不應有假承攬真僱傭的情況、假借其它契約形式來規避雇主應有責任。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>許銘春也提到，現代社會有很多新興型態經濟，為的是要解決人類的生活問題、給予方便，但希望企業能善盡社會責任，不要因為新興型態經濟而剝削勞動力、危害勞工工作安全。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/4175945</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class='fb-like 